title: New: Oscar Key Sung – It’s Coming / Sure Thing (Miguel Cover)
content:
It’s been a minute since we last heard from Melbourne multi-talented producer Oscar Key Sung, and what better way to announce your return than with a Miguel cover? The B-side to new single It’s Coming, Oscar Key Sung’s take on Sure Thing is choppy and slightly distracted at times, a fitting accompaniment to the flip-side, a soulful R&B number, that mixes his unconventional stylings with more modern, hip hop arrangements.

Check out both below.
